title: Paul Hollywood City Bakes S01E01-E10 PDTV.x264-TVCUK
description:
Britain's favourite baker, Paul Hollywood, is on a journey visiting some of the world's most vibrant destinations, visiting local bakeries and meeting the bakers who work there.



Episode Destinations

1.  New York
2.  Paris
3.  London
4.  St. Petersburg
5.  Naples, Italy
6.  Copenhagen
7.  Madrid
8.  Warsaw
9.  Miami
10. Munich




Original Air Dates: 18-Apr-2016 to 16-May-2016
